HEADWORD: Whoever
<hw>Who*ev"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>pron.</pos> <def>Whatever person;
any person who; be or she who; any one who; <as>as, he shall be
punished, <ex>whoever</ex> he may be</as>.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Whoever</xex> envies or repines.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Milton.</au>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Whoever</xex> the king favors.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

